#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_f.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral\\_f"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_f.noncentral_f:1 of
msgid "Draw samples from the noncentral F distribution."
msgstr "从非中心 F 分布中抽取样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_f.noncentral_f:3 of
msgid ""
"Samples are drawn from an F distribution with specified parameters, "
"`dfnum` (degrees of freedom in numerator) and `dfden` (degrees of freedom"
" in denominator), where both parameters > 1. `nonc` is the non-centrality"
" parameter."
msgstr ""
"样本从具有指定参数的 F 分布中抽取，`dfnum`（分子自由度）和 `dfden`（分母"
"自由度）均大于 1。`nonc` 是非中心参数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_f.noncentral_f of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_f.noncentral_f:8 of
msgid "Numerator degrees of freedom, should be > 0."
msgstr "分子自由度，应大于 0。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_f.noncentral_f:10 of
msgid "Denominator degrees of freedom, should be > 0."
msgstr "分母自由度，应大于 0。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_f.noncentral_f:12 of
msgid ""
"Non-centrality parameter, the sum of the squares of the numerator means, "
"should be >= 0."
msgstr "非中心参数，是分子均值平方和，应大于等于 0。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_f.noncentral_f:15 of
msgid ""
"Output shape.  If the given shape is, e.g., ``(m, n, k)``, then ``m * n *"
" k`` samples are drawn.  If size is ``None`` (default), a single value is"
" returned if ``dfnum``, ``dfden``, and ``nonc`` are all scalars.  "
"Otherwise, ``np.broadcast(dfnum, dfden, nonc).size`` samples are drawn."
msgstr ""
"输出形状。如果给定形状如 ``(m, n, k)``，则抽取 ``m * n * k`` 个样本。如果"
" size 是 ``None``（默认），且 ``dfnum``、``dfden`` 和 ``nonc`` 都是标量，"
"则返回一个单一值。否则，抽取 ``np.broadcast(dfnum, dfden, nonc).size`` 个"
"样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_f.noncentral_f:21 of
msgid "Desired chunk size on each dimension"
msgstr "每个维度上期望的块大小"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_f.noncentral_f:23 of
msgid "Allocate the tensor on GPU if True, False as default"
msgstr "如果为 True，则将张量分配到 GPU 上，默认为 False"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_f.noncentral_f:25 of
msgid "Data-type of the returned tensor."
msgstr "返回张量的数据类型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_f.noncentral_f of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_f.noncentral_f:28 of
msgid ""
"**out** -- Drawn samples from the parameterized noncentral Fisher "
"distribution."
msgstr "**out** -- 从参数化的非中心 Fisher 分布中抽取的样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_f.noncentral_f of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_f.noncentral_f:32 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_f.noncentral_f:33 of
msgid ""
"When calculating the power of an experiment (power = probability of "
"rejecting the null hypothesis when a specific alternative is true) the "
"non-central F statistic becomes important.  When the null hypothesis is "
"true, the F statistic follows a central F distribution. When the null "
"hypothesis is not true, then it follows a non-central F statistic."
msgstr ""
"在计算实验功效（功效 = 当特定备择假设为真时拒绝原假设的概率）时，非中心 F"
" 统计量变得重要。当原假设为真时，F 统计量服从中心 F 分布。当原假设不成立"
"时，则服从非中心 F 分布。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_f.noncentral_f:40 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_f.noncentral_f:41 of
msgid ""
"Weisstein, Eric W. \"Noncentral F-Distribution.\" From MathWorld--A "
"Wolfram Web Resource. http://mathworld.wolfram.com/NoncentralF-"
"Distribution.html"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_f.noncentral_f:44 of
msgid ""
"Wikipedia, \"Noncentral F-distribution\", http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki"
"/Noncentral_F-distribution"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_f.noncentral_f:48 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.noncentral_f.noncentral_f:49 of
msgid ""
"In a study, testing for a specific alternative to the null hypothesis "
"requires use of the Noncentral F distribution. We need to calculate the "
"area in the tail of the distribution that exceeds the value of the F "
"distribution for the null hypothesis.  We'll plot the two probability "
"distributions for comparison."
msgstr ""
"在一项研究中，检验相对于原假设的特定备择假设需要使用非中心 F 分布。我们"
"需要计算分布尾部超过原假设下 F 分布值的区域。我们将绘制两个概率分布进行"
"比较。"

